column1: IF ccr_l8_oh_tha_d is MF 0 AND ccr_l6a_oh_dha_d is MF 0 AND ccr_etio_d is MF 0 THEN 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 0
IF ccr_pt_one_d is MF 2 AND ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 2 THEN 4_Obese is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 0
IF ccr_sa_dihydrotest_d is MF 1 AND ccr_s_ad_17b_d is MF 1 THEN 1_SousPoid is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
IF ccr_sa_thf_d is MF 1 AND ccr_testosterone_d is MF 0 THEN 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 0
IF ccr_thaldo_d is MF 0 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 4_Obese is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 1
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 0  2_Normal is 1  3_Surpoid is 1  4_Obese is 0  5_ExtremeObese is 1
